oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Carte de visite of Elizabeth "Betsy" T. Teague
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Betsy Teague of Moscow, Fayette County, Tenn. was the mother of three Confederate soldiers: Pvt. Benjamin Franklin Teague, Co. E, 13th Tenn. Inf., CSA, Pvt. James Teague, Co. L, 2nd Partisan Rangers, Miss. Cav., CSA, and Pvt. Jeff Teague, Co. C, 20th Tenn. (Nixon's) Cav., CSA.
